\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"coverage\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 463}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"the colours\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"our national sporting colours\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Why do we have a red, white and blue flag, and yet our national colours are green and gold,\\\" Elliott asked.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Elliott\", \"score\": 0.9675856365381578, \"rank\": 0.01903464585615815, \"text\": \"Elliott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Elliott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Elliott\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a red, white and blue flag\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 619}, {\"ngram\": \"our national colours\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Melbourne radio host said it raised the question of whether the Australian flag should be changed before he proposed a design based on the symbol of a Kangaroo.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 691, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9475804215393344, \"rank\": 0.05455809511896677, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the question\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"a design\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"the symbol\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"a Kangaroo\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The kangaroo is the quintessential symbol of Australia,\\\" he said \\\"If you wanted to unite our sporting colours of green and gold, I reckon a flag that would make sense would be a green background with the yellow kangaroo in the centre.\\\"\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9701977993334598, \"rank\": 0.0274703247962162, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The kangaroo\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"the quintessential symbol\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"our sporting colours\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"green\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"a flag\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"a green background\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"the yellow kangaroo\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Melbourne radio host pointed out the famous green and gold boxing kangaroo flag was flown during Australia's historic victory in the America's Cup.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1096, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9475804215393344, \"rank\": 0.05455809511896677, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 1194, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res